The following format are supported.

2001-02-03T04:05:06Z
2001-02-03T04:05:06.1Z
2001-02-03T04:05:06.12Z
2001-02-03T04:05:06.123Z
2001-02-03T04:05:06.123456Z
2001-02-03T04:05:06.123456789Z
